item.title: Prayer bpn12995 in Daga
item.description: *U’ura ma marek iyanupe wainapen. Marek iyanupe aeni usu marek ae visen. Iwa Maman iup megawa. Namu pusin nanin ge ginan namun bigi warat amba toentanet tanam arige gambenaen yonat wat. Ne ipiri wakakayatsiagin, O Ayop negawa Ge tavenat nimanegeyan menan, Ge ne imuwasuat negawa inagap amba Genan aeamat taigain. Ne ipiri wakakayatsiagin endi mari, ne aroyan uon amba Ge amun gega gapan. Ne vidi gorowa orup da amba Ge enpuraput iapanewa.
